formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1 Form-2 of Engineer Certificate is upated with Form-3 of CA Certificate till date of BUC date(14.12.2017). The physical visit of Engineer is upto the date of BUC Date. There after no data addition in engineer certificate(Form-2).				
2 Amount reported at Sr. No. 7 is actual amount received from customers towards booking and sale of offices but excludes all taxes collected from customers.				
				
3 Above figures are certified based on posting in books of accounts as on 31/07/2019. The details in Annexure-A are also as on 31/07/2019.				
				
4 Figures for the period from 01/04/2019 to 31/07/2019 included in above are based on provisional unaudited financial statements. 				
				
5 Figures for the period upto 31/03/2018 and 31/03/2019 included in above are extracted from financial statements not audited by any of the member of the Institute of Chartered Accounts of India.				
				
6 There are only three shops (407, 411, 501) in respect of which  Agreement of sale has been exucuted by the promotor. Therefore, in order to avoid error while uploading CA certificate on GujRERA website, date of 1st cheque received against those flats where no Agreement of sale has been executed mentioned in the column "Date of Agreement for Sale".
